- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 core patterns behind `#if NET7_0_OR_GREATER` (L13-24)
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()` (L159)
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `.ToLowerInvariant()` correctly (L189)
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` and `WordCount` use efficient foreach loops (L252, L277)

